An easy solution is indeed, as suggested by ProfoundlyOblivious to set an auto filter before:

    MySheet.Range(&quot;A6:L17&quot;).AutoFilter Field:=1, Criteria1:=&quot;=AAA&quot;

The restriction to only include visible fields into the range will do the rest.

To select more filters you can simply add them:

    MySheet.Range(&quot;A6:L17&quot;).AutoFilter Field:=1, Criteria1:=&quot;=AAA&quot;, Operator:=xlOr, Criteria2:=&quot;=BBB&quot;

